reviewText: Super funny and entertaining. Don't watch if you're offended by cross dressing or transgender issues. Also, don't watch if sensitive to full frontal nudity. Otherwise, a very imaginative way of making a musical. Funny, humoristic and very entertaining.

Something totally out of the ordinary. If you are into original and out of the ordinary entertainments, this is a must see film. Great, colorful, amuzing and an excesively creative film!!! GREAT PIECE...LOVED IT!
